data.description: Welcome to this great 2081 Sqft 3 bed 2 Bath home located on the 17th green of Pichacho Hills Country Club. Step inside to discover a tastefully upgraded interior, featuring elegant quartz and granite countertops throughout the home. The custom backsplashes add a touch of sophistication & charm, making this space perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet meals with loved ones. One of the highlights of this home is the delightful viewing deck, strategically positioned to offer breathtaking views of both sunrises and sunsets over the Organ Mountains, and the serene beauty of the golf course or unwinding after a long day with a picturesque sunset as your backdrop. With quartz countertops, custom backsplashes, a viewing deck, and an entertaining backyard, this home is an opportunity not to be missed. Indulge in the luxury of living amidst natural beauty and immerse yourself in the enchanting golf course lifestyle. Your dream home await
